<li>I cherish every memory we've made together. Happy Mother's Day!</li>
<li>Your love is a constant source of comfort and strength.</li>
<li>Happy Mother's Day to the most amazing woman I know.</li>
<li>To my incredible mom, thank you for everything.</li>
<li>Mom, you're my rock, my inspiration, and my best friend.</li>
