<li>Your love is the greatest gift I've ever received.</li>
<li>Thank you for always believing in me, Mom.</li>
<li>Happy Mother's Day to the most selfless person I know.</li>
<li>Wishing you a day filled with joy and happiness, Mom.</li>
    

